<br>
Demented came along and I spoke to one of the would be officers the night he landed here. Hell I thought he was my old friend come back from the grave so to speak. We spoke for a bit and he told me what they planned. I sat and watched for a little while to see if what he said was true. I asked around and asked some people that guilded with them and heard nothing but good things.<br>
<br>
A few days later we joined. To be honest with you...it was the best move I ever made. My wife and I have never been happier in a guild. Sure we have some folks that came from another server and are residing in other people toons. You know what though? I miss my old friend Groggle....he was a great guy. The new Groggle....he I consider a very good friend of mine. So on one hand I lost a friend when Grog quit playing. On the other hand I gained another good friend. I must also say that all of the people that made the trip over from their former servers and now inhabit someone else's toon in AD have become some great friends of mine. These folks are decent people and skilled at what they do. To be honest with you...I wouldn't trade them. They brought my wife and I something we were missing on FV. To those of you .....you know who you are, Thanks.<br>
<br>
Ebay doesn't hurt everyone. It has helped some of us in ways that weren't available at the time. I am sorry for you...those that are unhappy by this taking place. I wish there was a way to make things better for you but, My guild just wouldn't be the same without these people in it. I invite you to speak to them one on one sometime...see who they really are if you give a damn.Your choice....or you can continue your hatred of them for what they did. <br>
<br>
Life is what you make of it...even here in EQ.<br>
<br>
